com.epam.finaltask.service

Class AbstractService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epam.finaltask.service.AbstractService
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccountService, AuthenticationService, MessageService, RegistrationService, TopicService

    public abstract class AbstractService
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides basic service implementation. Contains daoFactory and connectionManagerFactory field and constructors to specify their content.
